oracle.pg.common.csvconverter

Class CSV2OPEConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.common.csvconverter.CSV2OPGConfigBase
      • oracle.pg.common.csvconverter.CSV2OPEConfig
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSV2OPGConfig

    public class CSV2OPEConfig
extends CSV2OPGConfigBase
    This class contains the configuration settings to convert a CSV file into an edge file in Oracle Flat-file format (OPE file).
